Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=30}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:22.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acho que isso serve...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.34,0:02:31.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Momoo! Hora de comer! Momoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.13,0:02:34.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's strange. - OG}Que estranho...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.09,0:02:37.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He should be starving by now... - OG}Ele deveria estar morrendo de fome\Njá a essa hora.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Onde será que ele foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Gen-san! - OG}Sr. Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:53.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The possession of weapons\Nis a clear sign of rebellion! - OG}{The possession of weapons\Nis a clear act of rebellion! - arch}Possuir armas\Né um claro ato de rebelião!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:56.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{To keep any more rebels\Nlike you from showing up, - OG}Para impedir que mais rebeldes\Ncomo você apareçam,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.45,0:03:01.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm going to kill you right now,\Nas an example to the other humans! - OG}Vou matar você agora mesmo\Ncomo exemplo para os outros humanos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:06.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No way! He'll kill someone\Njust for having a weapon?! - OG}Não! Ele vai matar alguém\Nsó por ter armas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.92,0:03:08.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele não tem esse direito!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:10.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-E-Ei, você! Ei! Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.34,0:03:13.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você não tem o direito de fazer isso, Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.30,0:03:21.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{For these past eight years straight,\Nwe've paid you your tribute money! - OG}{For eight years straight,\Nwe've paid your tribute money! - Gaijin}Pagamos o tributo pra você\Npor oito anos seguidos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Why would we want to\Nrebel now, of all times?! - OG}{Why would we suddenly\Nwant to rebel now?! - Gord}Por que de repente\Níamos querer nos rebelar {\i1}agora{\i0}?!{Gord+WF}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:26.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Take your hands off Gen-san! - OG}{Put Gen down! - Gord, he technically only has one hand on}Larga o Sr. Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:32.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's not like he used any weapons! - OG}Não é como se ele tivesse\Nusado alguma arma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:33.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Stop this! - OG}Pare com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.82,0:03:35.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let Gen-san go! - OG}Solte o Sr. Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:40.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Estou dizendo que possuir armas\Nindica a vontade de se rebelar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.58,0:03:44.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Or what? Shall the entire\Nvillage be destroyed? - OG}Talvez eu devesse riscar\Nesta vila do mapa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:50.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se um só de vocês levantar a mão contra nós,\Na vila será destruída.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:53.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Either way is fine with me! - OG}Tanto faz pra mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.05,0:03:55.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entrem todos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.80,0:04:00.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If we cause trouble now, the last\Neight years will be for nothing! - OG}Se causarmos problemas agora,\Nos últimos oito anos terão sido em vão!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.39,0:04:03.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you wanted to fight\Nto the death to defy his rule, - OG}Se quiséssemos lutar\Naté a morte em desafio,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{then you should've done so\Neight years ago instead! - OG}a hora de fazer isso\Nteria sido oito anos atrás!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.77,0:04:14.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But we all swore to fight\Nthe patient fight! To live! - OG}Todos juramos que aguentar\Nseria nossa luta. Juramos viver!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:16.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Gen-san! - OG}Sr. Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.57,0:04:20.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What a valuable opinion!\NYou're a great speaker! - OG}Que palavras sábias!\NVocê sabe fazer um discurso!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:23.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yes! Being alive is enjoyable! - OG}Sim! Estar vivo é uma coisa boa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:26.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Até para insetos insignificantes como vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Gen-san! - OG}Sr. Gen!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:34.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nem todos os seres vivos nascem iguais!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.42,0:04:37.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Maldito...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:37.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pare!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.76,0:04:41.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't do anything! - OG}Não toquem neles!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:42.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But, Gen-san! - OG}Mas, Sr. Gen...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:48.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Se você morrer, acabou tudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.23,0:04:50.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't stop fighting the patient fight! - OG}Não parem de lutar essa\Nbatalha de resistência!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:52.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Even if I die! - OG}Mesmo que eu morra...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.81,0:04:54.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's nice resolve! - OG}Bela determinação!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.94,0:04:57.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Prestem muita atenção, humanos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:05:02.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is what happens to those who\Nhave even a sliver of evil thoughts! - OG}Isso é o que acontece com aqueles que\Nmostram sequer um traço de rebeldia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:04.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Estrela Explosiva!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.79,0:05:09.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-O que foi aquilo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:12.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Olha! Lá em cima!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tem alguém no telhado!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:18.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem diabos é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:24.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Meu nome é Capitão Usopp,\Nbravo guerreiro do mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.06,0:05:27.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Him! - OG}{It's him! - Gaijin}É ele...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O mundo me teme
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e me chama de Rei Demônio Usopp,\No homem do submundo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If you run away now, I'll forgive you! - OG}Vou dar uma última\Nchance pra vocês fugirem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu tenho 8.000–
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Arlong-san! That's him! - OG}Capitão Arlong! É ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:41.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O cara que escapou antes!
Comment: 0,0:05:40.32,0:05:41.07,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Eep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.07,0:05:44.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Bring all the tens of thousands\Nof men you want. - OG}Traga dezenas de milhares\Nde homens se quiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:47.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vou despedaçar cada um deles!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:52.25,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's not scared, and\Nthe Exploding Star had no effect! - OG}Minha estrela explosiva não\Nassustou ele nem um pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.25,0:05:54.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What has a human... - OG}Como ousa um humano...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:58.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{a mere, lowly human... done to me?! - OG}um humano inferior e inútil\Nfazer isso comigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:06.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Arlong-san! Wait! - OG}Capitão Arlong! Espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:10.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We'll lose another source\Nof tribute money, after Gosa! - OG}{We'll lose another source\Nof income, like Gosa! - Gaijin}Vamos perder mais uma\Nfonte de dinheiro, como Gosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.02,0:06:16.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Human settlements are easy to\Ndestroy, but our goal is to rule them! - OG}Vilas humanas são fáceis de destruir,\Nmas nosso objetivo é governá-las!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:19.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{If we lose some, we can\Njust get some more! - OG}Se destruirmos algumas, arranjamos mais!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.36,0:06:23.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nós somos a espécie suprema!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now he's destroying the village! - OG}Ele está destruindo a vila!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.12,0:06:30.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele vai...?!
Comment: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Whoa! I'm gonna die! I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.83,0:06:33.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu vou morrer! Eu vou morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:36.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{H-He's still alive! After 'im! - OG}E-Ele ainda está vivo! Atrás dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.83,0:06:35.63,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:40.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Peguem e matem ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:43.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Hey! Let's get back to Arlong Park! - OG}Ei! Vamos levá-lo\Nde volta pro Arlong Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He's seriously about\Nto destroy the village! - OG}{If we don't, he'll destroy the village! - OG}Se isso continuar, ele vai destruir a vila!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.51,0:06:46.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.35,0:06:49.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Do not let him get away! - OG}Não deixem ele escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:51.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quem ele pensa que somos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.35,0:06:52.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We'll be back another day. - OG}{We'll be back soon. - Gord}Voltaremos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.48,0:06:55.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Looks like you're spared for now! - OG}Vocês vivem por enquanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:03.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me desculpem...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:05.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Causei problemas pra todos vocês...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Do que você está falando?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:08.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're not at fault here! - OG}Você não fez nada de errado!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:09.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.41,0:07:12.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But who was that youngster earlier? - OG}Mas quem era aquele jovem?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.95,0:07:14.46,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pessoal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:16.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Que bom ver vocês de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.46,0:07:18.50,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's Nacchan! - OG}É a Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É ela!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você nunca passa direto\Npela vila...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:33.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I heard a loud sound... - OG}Ouvi um barulho alto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:34.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Arlong, huh? - OG}Arlong, é...?
Comment: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:46.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Just...
Comment: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:48.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,seven million berries left to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.57,0:07:48.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Só mais sete milhões de berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:52.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You have as horrible\Na reputation as ever. - OG}Sua reputação continua horrível como sempre.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.83,0:07:55.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's fine. I am a pirate! - OG}Tudo bem. Eu sou pirata, afinal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But Arlong's a reasonable guy. - OG}O Arlong é surpreendentemente razoável.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:00.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Money will fix all this, - OG}{Money'll fix all this. - Gaijin}Dinheiro resolve tudo isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.25,0:08:03.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so it's just a little more until our agreement. - OG}{Just a bit more, and I meet\Nmy bargain with Arlong. - Gaijin}Estou quase cumprindo\Nmeu acordo com o Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.26,0:08:09.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No matter what, I'm going\Nto earn 100 million belly - OG}{Whatever it takes, I'm going\Nto earn 100 million belly - Gaijin}Custe o que custar,\Nvou juntar 100 milhões de berries
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:11.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,e comprar esta vila!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:19.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{She tells me to run, but I got\Nnowhere else to go but here... - OG}Ela me manda fugir, mas é exatamente\Naqui que eu devo estar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:23.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Plus, I promised Luffy\NI'd bring her back. - OG}Quer dizer, prometi pro Luffy\Nque traria aquela garota de volta.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:26.74,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What's he up to now? - OG}Bom, e o que eu faço agora?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:28.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Things're starting to get messy. - OG}As coisas estão começando a complicar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu falei, isso é meu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.92,0:08:43.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Tá bom, desculpa! Pode ficar com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Você sabe que eu não posso comer isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:47.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'm not a dog, you know! - OG}Eu não sou um cachorro, droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:49.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Silêncio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.89,0:08:58.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É grande...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:08:59.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What? - OG}Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que é aquilo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:13.62,Main-207-,,0,0,5,,Um monstro marinho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:16.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's a cow! It's huge! - OG}Aquela vaca é enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:20.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uma vaca? Elas não nadam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.25,0:09:21.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's a hippo. - OG}Deve ser um hipopótamo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:24.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que uma coisa dessas\Nestá fazendo no East Blue?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:27.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is a Grand Line creature! - OG}{It's a Grand Line monster! - Gord}É uma criatura da Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.76,0:09:30.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que esse bicho está fazendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele está atrás da comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:38.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:39.77,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Rápido, dá pra ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.77,0:09:41.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He'll flip the boat over! - OG}Ele vai virar o barco!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.14,0:09:43.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Gum-Gum Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.32,0:09:50.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Stay away from my food! - OG}Fica longe do meu almoço!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:52.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You did it!\NYou're incredible, Big Bro Luffy! - OG}Conseguiu! Incrível, Mano Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.37,0:09:57.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que você deixou ele furioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:09:59.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Another one, huh?! - OG}Quer mais?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:00.45,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Seu idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:03.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Don't beat up someone who's hungry for no reason! - OG}Não sai batendo à toa\Nnuma pobre criatura faminta!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.25,0:10:07.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele provavelmente está machucado\Ne não consegue pegar comida sozinho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.88,0:10:09.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Right? - OG}Não é mesmo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:11.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What love... - OG}Que fofo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Toma, come aí.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.26,0:10:15.51,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{No need to hold back. - OG}Não precisa ter vergonha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:23.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Die, you damn thing! - OG}Morra, desgraçado!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.23,0:10:30.48,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{What're you doing?!\NWhat happened to that love?! - OG}{What're you doing?!\NWhat happened to that sweetness?! - Gaijin}Pra que isso?!\NCadê aquela fofura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.48,0:10:33.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The bastard just tried to eat me, too. - OG}Aquele desgraçado ia me\Ncomer junto com a comida.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:39.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Here he comes!\NHe's gonna sink the boat! - OG}Lá vem ele! Vai afundar o barco!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Maldito!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sai de perto. Eu cuido disso.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:49.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Collier Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Maldito hipopótamo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:00.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{All right! Back to food! - OG}Beleza! De volta à comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That was good exercise. - OG}Não foi um mau exercício.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.60,0:11:04.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Esses caras são malucos...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.44,0:11:08.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que está demorando tanto?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Quando o Luffy vai aparecer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.78,0:11:18.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mais cinco minutos\Ne eu vou morrer de tédio!
Comment: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:21.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh! Oh! Oh!
Comment: 0,0:11:21.37,0:11:23.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh! Incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:28.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Not even Hatchan, major octopus\Nleader of the Arlong Pirates, can pull you up! - OG}{\q2}Nem mesmo Hatchan, grande oficial polvo\Ndos Piratas do Arlong, consegue te puxar!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're a super grade fish! - OG}Você é um peixe de categoria super!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:36.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Dunno who you are, but you're\Nthe gutsiest fish in the East Blue! - OG}Não sei quem você é, mas é o peixe\Nmais corajoso do East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:37.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Uau! Que...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:41.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Era eu esse tempo todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.31,0:11:47.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're indeed the gutsiest\Nfish in the East Blue, me. - OG}{I'm indeed the gutsiest fish\Nin the East Blue. - Gaijin}{I really am the gutsiest fish\Nin the East Blue. - Gord}Eu realmente sou o mais\Ncorajoso do East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:49.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Espera, isso não parece estranho?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.27,0:11:51.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Com certeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:54.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Quem é você?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.57,0:11:57.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.49,0:11:59.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sou o Hatchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.53,0:12:01.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Me chama de Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.41,0:12:03.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You a fishman, too? - OG}{You're a fishman, too? - Gord}Você também é um homem-peixe?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:07.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Of course, of course!\NI'm a fascinating octopus fishman! - OG}Claro, claro!\NEu sou um deslumbrante homem-peixe polvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.54,0:12:09.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Pelo jeito, você é humano?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:10.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,S-Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.58,0:12:13.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Um marinheiro? Ou talvez um visitante?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:14.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Visitante?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.42,0:12:18.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Acho que dá pra dizer que sou um visitante.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.01,0:12:20.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Arlong-san's not here right now, is he? - OG}O Capitão Arlong não está\Naqui agora, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:21.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não. Pra onde ele foi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:27.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Parece que tem um forasteiro\Nnarigudo correndo por aí.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{He locked up his friend here - OG}{Another one is already locked up here - arch}O Arlong foi pegá-lo\Nna Vila Cocoyashi
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:33.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and went to Cocoyashi Village to get this other guy. - OG}depois de prender o amigo dele aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.48,0:12:35.19,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Usopp, huh? - OG}Usopp, é...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.19,0:12:36.99,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Guess I'll save him for now. - OG}Acho que vou salvá-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.24,0:12:41.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Essa Vila Cocoyashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:42.99,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como eu chego lá?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.99,0:12:44.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Entra.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:48.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're a guest. - OG}Você é um visitante, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.58,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu te levo lá,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,espadachim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.26,0:13:06.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Droga! Não consigo despistá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.73,0:13:12.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-Onde ele está?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:17.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Who thinks Usopp-sama is too important\Nof a person to have die yet?! - OG}{\q2}{Who thinks the Unbelievable Usopp is too important to die yet?! - Gaijin}Quem aqui acha que a morte do Incrível Usopp\Nseria um grande desperdício de talento?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:18.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.70,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu! Eu! Eu! Eu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Fool! What are you thinking?! - OG}O que esse idiota está aprontando?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.87,0:13:25.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ah, vocês também acham?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:27.12,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu concordo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.04,0:13:34.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O-O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:38.71,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}Estrela de Ovo Letal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:51.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Howdya like that?! I guess fishmen\Naren't all they're cracked up to be! - OG}Que tal essa?! Parece que os\Nhomens-peixe não são tão superiores!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.23,0:13:53.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Looks like every one of 'em let\NCaptain Usopp escape! - OG}Parece que todos eles\Ndeixaram o Capitão Usopp escapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Eu não sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:10.66,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:11.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Thanks for your cheering! - OG}Obrigado pela torcida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.63,0:14:19.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{As you can see, I'm perfectly okay! - OG}Como podem ver, estou muito bem vivo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:26.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Cocoyashi Village. - OG}Aqui é a Vila Cocoyashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:29.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Arlong-san should be here. - OG}O Capitão Arlong deve estar aqui.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:30.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Great. Thanks. - OG}Hein? Ah, ótimo. Valeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:33.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,De nada! Tchau!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:39.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Opa! Acabei de lembrar,\Nesqueci de perguntar seu nome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:42.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Huh? Me? What are you asking\Nmy name again for? - OG}Hein? Eu? Por que está\Nperguntando meu nome de novo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.78,0:14:44.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É Hatchan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:46.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Volte sempre!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:48.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Strange guy. - OG}Que cara estranho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Q-Que diabos aconteceu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.93,0:15:07.68,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.72,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,meus irmãos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:16.31,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Roronoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:20.36,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê? O que está tentando dizer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Roronoa Zoro...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.57,0:15:24.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.57,0:15:26.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Caçador de Piratas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:28.82,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Did he come to collect my head?! - OG}Ele veio atrás da minha recompensa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.33,0:15:34.79,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Não, ele não veio... A-Aquele cara...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.58,0:15:36.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele era... o Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.92,0:15:37.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:42.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That haramaki guy\Nwe caught was Roronoa... - OG}Aquele cara de faixa na barriga\Nque pegamos era o Roronoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.76,0:15:49.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu peguei ele!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,M-Mas o que é isso?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.10,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{D-Don't tell me Zoro... - OG}I-Isso tudo foi o Zoro...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.52,0:16:03.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Catching this scum isn't\Nenough to satisfy my hunger! - OG}Pegar essa escória não é nem perto\No suficiente pra saciar minha fome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.07,0:16:08.32,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Y-Yeah, huh?!\NSo you should let me go! - OG}É-É, né?!\NEntão devia me soltar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Eu só estava cumprimentando antes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:12.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,É-É assim que fazemos na minha vila!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.54,0:16:18.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But you are one of Zoro's men. - OG}Mas você é um dos homens do Zoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.33,0:16:24.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Though, it's only natural for famous\Nbounty hunters to come after me. - OG}Bom, é natural que caçadores\Nde recompensa famosos venham atrás de mim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não me mate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:34.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I don't have anything to do with Zoro! - OG}Eu não tenho nada a ver\Ncom esse tal de Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.97,0:16:36.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Enough of your poor lies. - OG}Chega de mentiras descaradas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:39.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You stood up to Arlong-san, too. - OG}Você também enfrentou\No Capitão Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:41.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Doesn't look like you're\Ngoing to live either way. - OG}Parece que você\Nvai morrer de qualquer jeito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.94,0:16:47.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Ei! Na verdade,\No Zoro e eu somos bem íntimos!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:49.57,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Então tenta encostar um dedo em mim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.57,0:16:51.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Zoro não vai ficar parado!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:52.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:56.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ou seja, se eu te matar,\No Zoro vai voltar?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.96,0:17:00.08,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{N-No, you're wrong! - OG}N-Não, espera, não é isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.08,0:17:04.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Killing me'd be very bad!\NIf you keep me alive, Zoro'll show up! - OG}{Killing me would be very bad!\NIf you keep me alive, Zoro'll show up! - Gaijin}Me matar é uma péssima ideia! Se você\Nme manter vivo, o Zoro vai aparecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.09,0:17:07.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But if you don't keep me\Nalive, Zoro won't come! - OG}{If you kill me, Zoro won't come! - Gord, redundancy}Na verdade, o Zoro {\i1}só{\i0}\Nvai aparecer se me manter vivo!{PP+Gord}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Mas como exatamente o Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:12.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,escapou da nossa prisão?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:14.26,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Como assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:16.89,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que quero dizer é que\Nalguém {\i1}deixou{\i0} ele escapar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.18,0:17:19.81,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Arlong-san. - OG}Capitão Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:22.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Isso te parece plausível?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:27.23,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{\q2}{Perhaps Nami let Zoro infiltrate this\Nplace so he could take your head? - OG}Talvez a Nami tenha deixado o Zoro se infiltrar\Nno nosso território pra pegar sua cabeça?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:31.20,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{N-Now that you mention it,\NNami has been acting strange lately. - OG}A-Agora que você mencionou,\Na Nami estava agindo estranho antes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:34.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Yeah. She even helped Zoro\Nwhen he jumped into the water. - OG}É. Ela até salvou o Zoro\Nquando ele pulou na água.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que ela estava trabalhando\Ncom o Zoro desde o início...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:38.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{and tricked us all?! - OG}Ela nos enganou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.08,0:17:43.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Traição é a especialidade dela.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.67,0:17:45.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{That's enough of that! - OG}Já chega!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Quit discussing stuff based\Non a bunch of conjecture! - OG}{Don't go any further based on\Na bunch of conjecture! - Gaijin}Especulação não leva a lugar nenhum!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.26,0:17:53.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:55.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Cuidado com o que falam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:59.35,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I swore I was a member of this group... - OG}Oito anos atrás, eu fiz essa tatuagem...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:02.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{eight years ago, with this tattoo! - OG}como meu juramento de lealdade a esta tripulação!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.56,0:18:06.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Desculpa, desculpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.61,0:18:07.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It's only natural for you to be upset. - OG}Obviamente, te chateamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:15.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But rest easy.\NI don't suspect you one bit. - OG}{But relax, I don't suspect you one bit. - Gord}Mas relaxa. Eu não suspeito de você.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:18.95,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You and me've known each\Nother for eight years now! - OG}Nos conhecemos\Nhá oito anos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:22.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We were just a little on edge is all. - OG}A gente só ficou um pouco nervoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:24.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Certo, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:29.21,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{The ones we do need to get rid of\Nare Roronoa Zoro and his group! - OG}Os que precisamos eliminar\Nsão Roronoa Zoro e seu grupo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,E-Ei, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:33.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,F-Fala alguma coisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.84,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,N-Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:39.97,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{Zoro just had to go and do that... - OG}O Zoro tinha que causar problemas...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.93,0:18:44.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O que foi, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:49.44,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You seem a little pale. - OG}Você está um pouco pálida.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.11,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But, as for long-nose here... - OG}Quanto ao narigudo aqui...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.28,0:18:57.87,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,nem mesmo você pode salvá-lo agora.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.20,0:19:01.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Not after he's defied Arlong-san. - OG}Não depois de ter desafiado o Capitão Arlong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.04,0:19:02.16,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Até quando...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:05.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Até quando vocês vão\Nsuspeitar de mim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.29,0:19:08.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You're too smart, you see. - OG}Você é esperta demais, sabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.09,0:19:11.80,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I'll have the amount Arlong\Nand I agreed to soon! - OG}Estou quase com o dinheiro\Nque eu e o Arlong combinamos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:13.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que eu trairia vocês agora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:15.22,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I know. - OG}Eu sei muito bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.97,0:19:21.39,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You agreed eight years ago to buy\NCocoyashi Village from Arlong-san for 100 million belly. - OG}{\q2}que oito anos atrás você concordou em pagar\N100 milhões de berries ao Arlong pela Vila Cocoyashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.52,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{But I just can't make sense of it. - OG}Mas eu simplesmente não consigo entender.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:31.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You betrayed the villagers and\Nyour parent and only trust money, - OG}{You betrayed the villagers and your\Nparent, and you only trust money, - Gaijin}Você traiu sua mãe e\Nos moradores. Só confia em dinheiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:33.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{so why do you care so much\Nabout Cocoyashi Village? - OG}Por que se importa tanto\Ncom Cocoyashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.53,0:19:36.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Por que uma vilazinha tão insignificante?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:40.49,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Na verdade, eu encontrei isso...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.62,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,no seu quarto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.29,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I-Isso é...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.13,0:19:49.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,meu...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,C-Como assim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.55,0:19:54.09,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,O Usopp foi capturado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.09,0:19:57.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Sim! Levaram ele pro\NArlong Park há pouco tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:20:00.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Brave as he was,\Nthat youngster defied Arlong! - OG}Aquele jovem foi corajoso,\Nmas desafiou o Arlong!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.85,0:20:02.60,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Ele com certeza já está morto!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.06,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Damn. - OG}Droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.77,0:20:10.56,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Of all times to get caught, it had\Nto be after I killed some time there! - OG}Por que ele tinha que ser pego\Nlogo depois que passei aquele tempo lá?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.94,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Usopp! Stay alive! - OG}Usopp! Não morre!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:33.63,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Vai! Pro Arlong Park!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:49.27,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Aguenta aí, Nami!
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=31}===============================DIALOGUE============================
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{=28}============================SIGNS AND TITLE=========================
